# Migrate-explain — static SQL safety preview

Run `gofasta migrate up --explain --strict --json` before applying
any migration. No DB connection required.

Surface the `max_risk` field and every migration whose risk is
`data-loss`, `lock-and-fill`, `lock-and-rewrite`, or
`app-incompatibility`. Ask before running `gofasta migrate up` if
any high-severity warning fires.
